HEADWORD: Deadish
<hw>Dead"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Somewhat dead, dull, or lifeless;
deathlike.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The lips put on a <qex>deadish</qex> paleness.</q> <rj><qau>A.
